spec_data.Name: fedora-user-agent-chrome
spec_data.Description:
This package is used to automatically install the Fedora User Agent extension
for Google Chrome/Chromium browser from Chrome Web Store. This extension will
modify your User-Agent string to include Fedora branding.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 04:05:52 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: User-Agent Fedora branding for Google Chrome/Chromium browser
